# Agent Guardrails

- Work only on branch `feat/subconscious-outcome-loop` unless told otherwise.
- Never modify `~/.hermes/hermes-agent` or the Rust product repo.
- Never delete or overwrite live PostgreSQL summaries/sources; use prefixed fixtures + `finally` cleanup in tests.
- Never commit credentials, `.env`, cache files (`.npz`, `.hermes/`), or local artifacts.
- Do not patch Hermes core for plugin loading — use `kind: standalone` in `plugin.yaml`.
- Leave `memory.provider` empty; KnowWhere hooks coexist with Hindsight.
- Run `test_pipeline.py` before and after DB/plugin changes; new behavior needs `test_outcome_loop.py`.
- Commit only when explicitly requested with the agreed message format.
